I've spoken to the director.

00:02:50.703 --> 00:02:52.639 line:95%,end
And you should, in no way, shape, or form,

00:02:52.705 --> 00:02:54.207 line:95%,end
hold that against Chloe.

00:02:54.274 --> 00:02:55.408 line:95%,end
[laughs]

00:02:56.109 --> 00:02:58.111 line:95%,end
Or at least I would think
you should know that.

00:02:58.178 --> 00:02:59.812 line:95%,end
I would think your mother
would have taught you better.

00:03:02.315 --> 00:03:05.418 line:95%,end
OK, I'm going to go in
because this is my job

00:03:05.485 --> 00:03:06.986 line:95%,end
and I am to be here.

00:03:14.360 --> 00:03:16.496 line:95%,end
Hey. Hello.

00:03:16.563 --> 00:03:18.531 line:95%,end
- Hi.
- How's it going?

00:03:18.598 --> 00:03:20.867 line:95%,end
- I heard you were talking to Abby.
- No, I was talking at Abby.

00:03:20.934 --> 00:03:24.270 line:95%,end
- She won't speak to me.
- Oh. Sometimes it's better that way.

00:03:24.337 --> 00:03:26.806 line:95%,end
That woman thinks that I'm going
to give her the time of day.

00:03:26.873 --> 00:03:29.275 line:95%,end
How dare her even walk into this studio.

00:03:29.342 --> 00:03:32.946 line:95%,end
She has [bleep] big [bleep] like a man,

00:03:33.012 --> 00:03:34.080 line:95%,end
because that's what she is.

00:03:34.147 --> 00:03:36.015 line:95%,end
She is disgusting.

00:03:36.082 --> 00:03:37.450 line:95%,end
Where have you been?

00:03:37.517 --> 00:03:39.018 line:95%,end
What have you been up to?

00:03:39.085 --> 00:03:41.054 line:95%,end
I don't know. We'll talk upstairs.

00:03:43.423 --> 00:03:45.358 line:95%,end
No need for applause. Let's go.

00:03:45.425 --> 00:03:46.993 line:95%,end
[laughs]

00:03:47.060 --> 00:03:48.361 line:95%,end
When I come back in the studio,

00:03:48.428 --> 00:03:50.597 line:95%,end
everyone's really excited
to see me, except Kelly,

00:03:50.663 --> 00:03:52.398 line:95%,end
and you would think that Kelly
should've been the one


00:03:52.465 --> 00:03:53.800 line:95%,end
who is most excited to see me.

00:03:54.467 --> 00:03:55.735 line:95%,end
All right.

00:03:55.802 --> 00:03:59.405 line:95%,end
You know, they told me that
Detroit was a tough city.

00:04:00.039 --> 00:04:01.808 line:95%,end
Well, it was.

00:04:02.508 --> 00:04:04.210 line:95%,end
You weren't the big winners.

00:04:04.277 --> 00:04:05.378 line:95%,end
You got beat.

00:04:05.445 --> 00:04:08.314 line:95%,end
Your champion winner will be
"Top of the World" entry number

00:04:08.381 --> 00:04:09.415 line:95%,end
89.

00:04:12.852 --> 00:04:14.187 line:95%,end
Third place.

00:04:14.254 --> 00:04:17.223 line:95%,end
Cathy is a fake and a phony.

00:04:17.590 --> 00:04:19.259 line:95%,end
She calls herself a choreographer?

00:04:19.325 --> 00:04:23.363 line:95%,end
She's an embarrassment to my vocation.

00:04:23.930 --> 00:04:28.668 line:95%,end
I think the loss to Cathy's
all-boy team was tough on Abby.

00:04:28.735 --> 00:04:30.803 line:95%,end
To be honest with you,
I think she did not like

00:04:30.870 --> 00:04:33.273 line:95%,end
losing to a group of all boys.

00:04:33.339 --> 00:04:36.809 line:95%,end
And then we had a duet,
but I can't really talk about it

00:04:36.876 --> 00:04:38.911 line:95%,end
because it didn't happen.

00:04:38.978 --> 00:04:40.146 line:95%,end
I pulled the duet.

00:04:40.213 --> 00:04:44.684 line:95%,end
If your mother is out of control,
you don't dance.

00:04:44.751 --> 00:04:46.219 line:95%,end
And Abby, that is fine.

00:04:46.286 --> 00:04:48.388 line:95%,end
I do want it noted on your record

00:04:48.454 --> 00:04:52.091 line:95%,end
that I was defending my daughter
because you were being insensitive

00:04:52.158 --> 00:04:53.493 line:95%,end
about her health issues.

00:04:53.559 --> 00:04:55.662 line:95%,end
That's what my disagreement with you was.

00:04:55.728 --> 00:04:58.798 line:95%,end
So let's just say I'm not
putting up with it anymore.

00:05:01.501 --> 00:05:03.736 line:95%,end
We've had a member of the team suspended.

00:05:04.504 --> 00:05:06.039 line:95%,end
You all know what suspended is.

00:05:07.006 --> 00:05:09.609 line:95%,end
It's like the last
chance before dismissal.

00:05:11.444 --> 00:05:13.046 line:95%,end
Let's move on to the pyramid.

00:05:13.112 --> 00:05:15.982 line:95%,end
Chloe, obviously,
you were not on the pyramid.

00:05:16.482 --> 00:05:19.118 line:95%,end
On the bottom, Nia.

00:05:19.185 --> 00:05:20.653 line:95%,end
You should have expected to be there.

00:05:23.856 --> 00:05:28.261 line:95%,end
Paige kind of got thrown
under the bus with the duet.

00:05:28.328 --> 00:05:32.065 line:95%,end
Next we have Kendall.

00:05:32.131 --> 00:05:34.901 line:95%,end
Now Kendall, you were given a solo.

00:05:35.301 --> 00:05:37.570 line:95%,end
You didn't even make the top 10.

00:05:37.637 --> 00:05:39.972 line:95%,end
Alexandra, "Below Zero."

00:05:43.209 --> 00:05:45.445 line:95%,end
Do I just keep giving you a solo?

00:05:45.511 --> 00:05:47.246 line:95%,end
No.

00:05:47.313 --> 00:05:49.982 line:95%,end
Next, Mackenzie.

00:05:50.049 --> 00:05:52.018 line:95%,end
I told you I wasn't going
to put you in the groups anymore

00:05:52.085 --> 00:05:54.153 line:95%,end
because you are the weak link.

00:05:55.688 --> 00:05:57.557 line:95%,end
This time I thought you were excellent.

00:05:59.392 --> 00:06:02.862 line:95%,end
And moving next, Brooke.

00:06:03.429 --> 00:06:05.498 line:95%,end
It was the first time you
were officially on the team.

00:06:10.703 --> 00:06:13.306 line:95%,end
I thought the parts
that you did in the routine

00:06:13.373 --> 00:06:16.075 line:95%,end
that were your solo spots were excellent.

00:06:17.477 --> 00:06:22.014 line:95%,end
But I need you still to be more
of a role model, understood?

00:06:23.883 --> 00:06:27.120 line:95%,end
And at the top of the pyramid, Maddie.

00:06:27.186 --> 00:06:29.088 line:95%,end
You have not had a solo for weeks.

00:06:29.155 --> 00:06:31.324 line:95%,end
Your highest scoring solo tonight

00:06:31.391 --> 00:06:33.826 line:95%,end
will be Maddie with "Quick Sand."

00:06:35.495 --> 00:06:37.330 line:95%,end
It's tough getting there.

00:06:37.397 --> 00:06:40.099 line:95%,end
It's even tougher staying there,
and you know that.

00:06:42.301 --> 00:06:45.838 line:95%,end
We will be attending In10sity Dance

00:06:45.905 --> 00:06:47.740 line:95%,end
in Fort Lauderdale, Florida.

00:06:49.308 --> 00:06:50.476 line:95%,end
[inaudible]

