Everybody will be in the group dance.

00:06:52.879 --> 00:06:55.515 line:95%,end
Now, the group routine
is a contemporary piece.

00:06:55.581 --> 00:07:01.154 line:95%,end
The name of the routine
is "Money is the Root of All Evil."

00:07:01.854 --> 00:07:03.723 line:95%,end
I really don't know
about the group routine this week,

00:07:03.790 --> 00:07:05.358 line:95%,end
"Money is the Root of All Evil."

00:07:05.425 --> 00:07:07.627 line:95%,end
I don't really equate money with evil.

00:07:07.693 --> 00:07:08.694 line:95%,end
Abby, yes.

00:07:08.761 --> 00:07:10.163 line:95%,end
Money, no.

00:07:10.229 --> 00:07:12.999 line:95%,end
Moms, the costumes are emerald green,

00:07:13.065 --> 00:07:15.902 line:95%,end
