actual real money on the costume.

00:07:26.446 --> 00:07:28.848 line:95%,end
I don't know about this idea
of putting real money

00:07:28.915 --> 00:07:29.982 line:95%,end
on these costumes.

00:07:30.049 --> 00:07:32.585 line:95%,end
We spend enough money
on costumes as it is.

00:07:32.652 --> 00:07:34.754 line:95%,end
This is going to be an expensive week.

00:07:34.821 --> 00:07:39.725 line:95%,end
Maddie, obviously, a solo is going to you.

00:07:39.792 --> 00:07:43.029 line:95%,end
And the other solo is going to Brooke.

00:07:43.429 --> 00:07:44.964 line:95%,end
[applause]


