for this competition season,

00:07:48.034 --> 00:07:49.402 line:95%,end
and Brooke needs the show Abby

00:07:49.469 --> 00:07:51.471 line:95%,end
that she wants to be part of this team.

00:07:51.537 --> 00:07:53.339 line:95%,end
I think she needs to go out there
and show her

00:07:53.406 --> 00:07:56.476 line:95%,end
that she still loves to dance
and she wants to be here.

00:07:56.542 --> 00:07:57.944 line:95%,end
We have a lot of work to do.

00:07:58.010 --> 00:08:01.280 line:95%,end
Moms, go ahead and go upstairs.

00:08:01.347 --> 00:08:03.483 line:95%,end
Spread apart. We're doing a whole warm-up.

00:08:06.619 --> 00:08:08.521 line:5%,start
Now ladies, think about this.

00:08:08.588 --> 00:08:10.289 line:5%,start
It's bluesy

00:08:10.356 --> 00:08:16.596 line:5%,start
so think of being in a speakeasy
or a nightclub.

00:08:16.662 --> 00:08:18.598 line:5%,start
"Money is the Root of All Evil"

00:08:18.664 --> 00:08:20.700 line:5%,start
is the name of our routine this week.

00:08:20.766 --> 00:08:23.302 line:5%,start
Now, the routine is contemporary,

00:08:23.369 --> 00:08:25.538 line:5%,start
but it has a little bit
of flamboyancy to it

00:08:26.038 --> 00:08:29.308 line:5%,start
and we're going to use real money
all over the costumes.

00:08:29.375 --> 00:08:33.012 line:95%,end
The faces have to come through,
and we need to bring it all

00:08:33.079 --> 00:08:35.781 line:95%,end
