00:08:37.149 --> 00:08:39.685 line:95%,end
5, 6, 7, go.

00:08:39.752 --> 00:08:42.088 line:95%,end
Duh, duh, duh, duh, duh, duh.

00:08:42.154 --> 00:08:44.056 line:95%,end
