00:09:17.790 --> 00:09:18.958 line:95%,end
and they wouldn't go into a bar.

00:09:19.025 --> 00:09:20.326 line:95%,end
Yeah, but there's no
such thing as a speakeasy.

00:09:20.393 --> 00:09:23.062 line:95%,end
- 90 years ago.
- Yeah, it doesn't exist.

00:09:23.129 --> 00:09:25.631 line:95%,end
I have to say, you know,
I wasn't here last week

00:09:25.698 --> 00:09:27.199 line:95%,end
and all of a sudden like I haven't

00:09:27.266 --> 00:09:29.435 line:95%,end
felt more like an
outsider in my life here.

00:09:30.303 --> 00:09:34.674 line:95%,end
It was a pretty quiet week relatively,
I would say, up until Saturday.

00:09:34.740 --> 00:09:37.643 line:95%,end
