I was in a Twilight Zone.

00:09:37.710 --> 00:09:39.045 line:95%,end
It was bizarre.

00:09:39.111 --> 00:09:40.246 line:95%,end
Just shut your mouth.

00:09:40.313 --> 00:09:42.048 line:95%,end
I didn't mean to do that.

00:09:42.114 --> 00:09:43.716 line:95%,end
I didn't mean to do that, either.

00:09:43.783 --> 00:09:44.917 line:95%,end
Get out.

00:09:44.984 --> 00:09:47.019 line:95%,end
You are a monstrosity of evil.

00:09:47.086 --> 00:09:48.321 line:95%,end
You're done. No duet.

00:09:48.387 --> 00:09:49.422 line:95%,end
It was bad.

00:09:49.488 --> 00:09:50.890 line:95%,end
I thought Saturday was just
a horrendous day all around.

00:09:50.957 --> 00:09:53.793 line:95%,end
So why weren't you answering
any of my phone calls

00:09:53.859 --> 00:09:55.494 line:95%,end
or my texts all week?

00:09:56.195 --> 00:09:58.230 line:95%,end
You called me once and I missed it.

