00:27:10.528 --> 00:27:13.298 line:95%,end
Sweet, pretty, little Maddie,

00:27:13.365 --> 00:27:16.635 line:95%,end
she's going to tell the judges
and every single person

00:27:16.701 --> 00:27:19.738 line:95%,end
